      "snippet": "Klay Thompson made history on Monday night. (Associated Press) The Golden State Warriors of the past three seasons are famous for setting records. They’ve won 73 games in a regular season, had ",
      "date": "2016-12-06 19:43:12"
    },
    {
      "title": "历史第一!康神轰26118迎里程碑 6记三分终结尼克斯7连胜",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_59469c5de2906752",
      "snippet": "class=\"video_iframe\" data-cover=\"http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-2895971200-59669477B1B33E940C3C692C1C9FF429/0?fmt=jpg&size=31&h=280&w=496&ppv=1\" height=\"375\" width=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//v.qq.com/iframe/player4qq.html?vid=m1260f24488&width=500&height=375&auto=0&rowkey=19069c5e0b2732KH\" scrolling=\"no\" data-aigc-mark=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>北京时间3月27日,NBA常规赛黄蜂主场114-103击败尼克斯,黄蜂豪取5连胜并且终结尼克斯的7连胜,康-克努佩尔全场14投9中､三分10中6轰下26分11篮板8助攻,一战连创多项历史纪录｡",
      "date": "2026-03-27 09:32:26"
